# Automated Valuation Engine — Implementation Walkthrough

## Overview

Implemented a production-ready, server-side valuation engine that automatically calculates creator/business asset valuations when users submit the `/valuation` or `/sell` forms. The engine integrates seamlessly with the existing Next.js 16 + Supabase architecture without modifying any UI or existing form fields.

