## Valuation Formula

### Step 1: Revenue Value
```
revenueValue = monthlyRevenue × revenueMultiplier
```

| Revenue Tier | Threshold | Multiplier |
|---|---|---|
| Premium | > $5,000 | 36× |
| Good | > $1,000 | 30× |
| Average | > $250 | 24× |
| Low | ≤ $250 | 18× |

### Step 2: Audience Value
```
audienceValue = audienceSize × platformRate
```

| Platform | Rate per follower |
|---|---|
| YouTube | $0.12 |
| Instagram | $0.05 |
| Twitter/X | $0.04 |
| Telegram | $0.03 |
| Default | $0.03 |

### Step 3: Base Value
```
baseValue = max(revenueValue, audienceValue)
```

### Step 4: Apply Multipliers
```
estimatedValue = baseValue × engagement × niche × country × age × monetization
```

### Step 5: Range
```
lowRange  = estimatedValue × 0.85
highRange = estimatedValue × 1.15
```

